{"tid":977204,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"有錢任性？Benz泊巴士總站　網民讚有膽識","createTime":"2019-01-11T04:29:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T19:21:28.000Z","uid":225464,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"86de51ff0c0902188dc1d55c3b33ea723101a0a9","tid":977204,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T04:29:28.000Z","msg":"<strong>【總是任性？P牌車泊巴士總站　網民讚有膽識】</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190111/bkn-20190111121058308-0111_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190111%2Fbkn-20190111121058308-0111_00822_001.html&d=48mk7pwonB40V2PL3zWGtl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=23023a10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190111/bkn-20190111121058308-0111_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NLfBUSK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNLfBUSK.jpg&h=d1f5b93b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d8524fbf2196a80656f224d20e259763e028037","tid":977204,"uid":225464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T04:29:32.000Z","msg":"香港地泊位難求，苦尋得空位又可能地方狹窄。有P牌平治司機索性泊在巴士總站，難道是貪其位置方便又寬敞？<br />\n<br />\n有網民周五（11日）在Facebook群組「小心駕駛（討論別人駕駛態度）」上載照片，只見在長沙灣海麗邨的巴士總站內，有一輛巴士無法靠站，原來有一輛掛上P牌的平治私家車竟泊上行人路，更在車道突出部分車身。當時車內未見司機，兩名警員到場了解事件。<br />\n<br />\n不少人諷刺司機：「P牌都咁大膽，收番個牌啦」、「唔係巴士公司車入巴士站，阻唔阻人都可以即抄啦」，又笑言︰「車牌同牌子說明一切」。"},{"pid":"4cce01566868092c40107b5b94c7ddcd40b65055","tid":977204,"uid":5967,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T04:31:18.000Z","msg":"P牌加v牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"275e2c82394e5e011eb47d4078b0339e5a2451a2","tid":977204,"uid":89538,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4cce01566868092c40107b5b94c7ddcd40b65055","tid":977204,"uid":5967,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTim